---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Hollywood's Shadowy Stars: Scandals Unveiled" description="Dive into the enigmatic world of Tinseltown's biggest names, where glamour hides gritty secrets and every spotlight casts long shadows. Explore profiles of iconic stars entangled in the web of Hollywood's darkest tales.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#0c1445] via-[#0c1445]/80 to-[#d90074]/20 z-0"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 60 60" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"%3E%3Cg fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"%3E%3Cg fill="%23d90074" fill-opacity="0.05"%3E%3Ccircle cx="30" cy="30" r="2"/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E')] z-0"></div>
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-24 md:py-32 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 mb-4 bg-[#d90074]/20 rounded-full border border-[#d90074]/30">
          <span class="text-[#d90074] font-bold tracking-wider">STAR GOSSIP CENTRAL</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          Hollywood's <span class="text-[#d90074]">Shadowy Stars</span>: Scandals Unveiled
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
          Dive into the enigmatic world of Tinseltown's biggest names, where glamour hides gritty secrets and every spotlight casts long shadows.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
          <button class="px-8 py-3 bg-[#d90074] text-white font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-[#b70061] transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 border border-[#d90074]">
            Explore Profiles
          </button>
          <button class="px-8 py-3 bg-transparent text-white font-bold rounded-lg border-2 border-[#d90074] hover:bg-[#d90074]/10 transition-all duration-300">
            Latest Scandals
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-16 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#0c1445] to-transparent z-10"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#0c1445] to-[#0c1445]/80">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
          In the Neon Haze of <span class="text-[#d90074]">Star Gossip Central</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
          <div class="w-24 h-0.5 bg-[#d90074] mx-2"></div>
          <i class="fas fa-star text-[#d90074] text-xl mx-2"></i>
          <div class="w-24 h-0.5 bg-[#d90074] mx-2"></div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          We peel back the velvet curtain on the icons who define Hollywood's <em class="text-[#d90074]">noir</em> underbelly. These aren't just celebritiesâ€”they're enigmas wrapped in scandal, their lives a cocktail of fame, fortune, and forbidden whispers.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Featured Stars Grid -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-[#0a0f33]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Featured Icons of Intrigue</h2>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-[#d90074] mx-auto"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Star Card 1 -->
        <div class="group bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0c1445]/70 to-[#0c1445]/40 rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-[#d90074]/20 hover:border-[#d90074]/50 transition-all duration-500 transform hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start mb-4">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[#d90074] to-[#b70061] flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold mr-4">
                MM
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Marilyn Monroe</h3>
                <p class="text-[#d90074] font-bold">The Eternal Blonde Bombshell</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">The playful pout masked a torrent of studio betrayals and rumored affairs with presidents. Did her untimely end hide a deeper conspiracy?</p>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-[#d90074]/20 text-[#d90074] rounded-full text-sm">Scandal</span>
              <i class="fas fa-chevron-right text-[#d90074] group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="h-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#d90074] to-[#b70061] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Star Card 2 -->
        <div class="group bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0c1445]/70 to-[#0c1445]/40 rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-[#d90074]/20 hover:border-[#d90074]/50 transition-all duration-500 transform hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start mb-4">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[#d90074] to-[#b70061] flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold mr-4">
                HB
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Humphrey Bogart</h3>
                <p class="text-[#d90074] font-bold">The Anti-Hero of Hollywood</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">The rugged anti-hero of the silver screen, whose off-screen feuds with Warner Bros. executives revealed the cutthroat casting couch of old Hollywood.</p>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-[#d90074]/20 text-[#d90074] rounded-full text-sm">Power Struggle</span>
              <i class="fas fa-chevron-right text-[#d90074] group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="h-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#d90074] to-[#b70061] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Star Card 3 -->
        <div class="group bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0c1445]/70 to-[#0c1445]/40 rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-[#d90074]/20 hover:border-[#d90074]/50 transition-all duration-500 transform hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start mb-4">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[#d90074] to-[#b70061] flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold mr-4">
                ET
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Elizabeth Taylor</h3>
                <p class="text-[#d90074] font-bold">The Violet-Eyed Vixen</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">A violet-eyed vixen whose eight marriages were mere facades for lavish lifestyles and hidden scandals that shake the foundations of Tinseltown.</p>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-[#d90074]/20 text-[#d90074] rounded-full text-sm">Marriage Drama</span>
              <i class="fas fa-chevron-right text-[#d90074] group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="h-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#d90074] to-[#b70061] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Interactive Spotlight -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#0c1445] to-[#0c1445]/80">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1a225d] to-[#0b1340] rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-[#d90074]/30 shadow-2xl">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
          <div class="md:w-1/3 mb-8 md:mb-0 flex justify-center">
            <div class="relative">
              <div class="w-48 h-48 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[#d90074] to-[#b70061] flex items-center justify-center">
                <i class="fas fa-moon text-white text-6xl"></i>
              </div>
              <div class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[#d90074] flex items-center justify-center animate-pulse">
                <i class="fas fa-star text-white"></i>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-2/3 md:pl-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">The <span class="text-[#d90074]">Hollywood</span> Spotlight</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
              Every star's journey is a tale of ambition, betrayal, and enduring mystery. The Hollywood spotlight may illuminate their faces, but it's the shadows that reveal their true nature. From the golden age of cinema to today's digital age, these stories of triumph and tragedy continue to captivate the world.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
              <button class="px-6 py-3 bg-[#d90074] text-white font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-[#b70061] transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105">
                Read Full Stories
              </button>
              <div class="flex items-center text-gray-400">
                <i class="fas fa-clock mr-2"></i>
                <span>Latest Updates</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quote Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-[#0a0f33]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <i class="fas fa-quote-left text-[#d90074] text-5xl mb-6"></i>
        <blockquote class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          "In Hollywood, even the brightest stars cast the longest shadows."
        </blockquote>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg">- The Star Gossip Central Chronicles</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#0c1445] to-[#d90074]/10">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Join the <span class="text-[#d90074]">Investigation</span></h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Become a part of Hollywood's most exclusive circle. Subscribe to our exclusive scandals newsletter and never miss a whisper from Tinseltown's shadowy corners.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4 max-w-xl mx-auto">
          <input 
            type="email" 
            placeholder="Enter your email" 
            class="px-6 py-4 bg-[#0c1445] border border-[#d90074]/30 rounded-lg text-white placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#d90074] flex-grow"
          >
          <button class="px-8 py-4 bg-[#d90074] text-white font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-[#b70061] transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 whitespace-nowrap">
            Subscribe Now
          </button>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-6">Join 10,000+ subscribers getting the dirtiest secrets</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>